{"tid":2125593,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"綜藝咖女星外型太火辣！　竟遭網友揚言威脅：「要強暴妳」","createTime":"2020-07-26T09:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T10:47:20.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f0144e9c635bc5090b9bcd1d91f1e5798e3cd0eb","tid":2125593,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:31:19.000Z","msg":"南韓綜藝咖女星姜藝彬（강예빈），雖演出過戲劇不過有個「牛鞭妹」的暱稱，有著E級棒的惹火身材，參與綜藝節目時經常以性感形象示人，她去年還曾來MTV台節目《拜託了! 女神Oh! My Venus》，介紹美妝與被突襲檢查包包，親民大方個性卻反而帶來負面影響，幾年前就曾傳出她在節目自爆，曾有網友留言威脅，讓她嚇得好一陣子都不敢出門。<br />\n<br />\n姜藝彬過去曾在記者活動上，穿著低胸小禮服下滑，瞬間性感爆乳而嬌羞，還以銷魂表情「大啖牛鞭」而爆紅，雄偉豪乳和渾圓飽滿的蜜桃臀，奪下韓國男人性幻想對象冠軍，甚至不少男性觀眾寫信要求電視台，一定要讓她爆乳上節目，因此雖然她被歸類為綜藝咖，不過節目中火辣程度，絲毫不輸給寫真女星。<br />\n<br />\n然而這反而讓姜藝彬造成威脅，她就曾自爆有網友上網留言威脅，她說：「那篇文章不但說要強暴我，還寫：『到現在都沒人對她出手，看來我們韓國男人太善良了。』讓我當時嚇到不敢出門，連收快遞都不敢開門」然而對方很快就將文章刪除，雖然她大受打擊，不過只能認定該網友已在反省，因此沒有提告，不過仍心有餘悸。"},{"pid":"f07f3c878e7068db33589105f179a46e369c91b9","tid":2125593,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/26/2684800-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F26%2F2684800-XXL.jpg&h=64e73399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼南韓女星姜藝彬京常以火辣性感造型示人。（圖／翻攝自姜藝彬IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/26/2684801-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F26%2F2684801-XXL.jpg&h=ff427ff6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61cad037dbb43f2e0e2dd550d78fd00a34eba89d","tid":2125593,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/05/31/1952146-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F05%2F31%2F1952146-XXL.jpg&h=70292bbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲南韓綜藝女神姜藝彬曾上過《拜託了! 女神》節目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/26/2684802-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F26%2F2684802-XXL.jpg&h=88dcad06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲姜藝彬火辣好身材「高深莫測」。（圖／翻攝自姜藝彬IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/26/2684805-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F26%2F2684805-XXL.jpg&h=fc444489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲姜藝彬爆曾遭因形象太性感，網友威脅要強暴她。（圖／翻攝自姜藝彬IG）"},{"pid":"32aa2ff78118eadff4e39324a12d278a924a2b7a","tid":2125593,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:32:49.000Z","msg":"個樣好老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8888e1466dc1c6e274b15b0a9b819dcb9cd7b595","tid":2125593,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/b1/42/03/b142031944b26e0e6329dd902723873c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fb1%2F42%2F03%2Fb142031944b26e0e6329dd902723873c.gif&h=27a08ca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/O8wBGGF-ygRjvAiCBFaXagcNmIyL5xHLWCX2a0lcu9Jen3l4P4tuaTVckaQ-nefkSSq24vAHN5kQ9avFAKfrlsqoCTNAScdT-kh8OV5C3oJYQGj3yvf5IgRmPnLN8r_e1vWwm7nYojafCV36r_yg1hZ4NKDlxCaAQGY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FO8wBGGF-ygRjvAiCBFaXagcNmIyL5xHLWCX2a0lcu9Jen3l4P4tuaTVckaQ-nefkSSq24vAHN5kQ9avFAKfrlsqoCTNAScdT-kh8OV5C3oJYQGj3yvf5IgRmPnLN8r_e1vWwm7nYojafCV36r_yg1hZ4NKDlxCaAQGY&h=c692b8d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n姜藝彬(37)"},{"pid":"de0190cdc8e47530a02aa595ce1336e384248c92","tid":2125593,"uid":297949,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:33:48.000Z","msg":"膠到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"